episodes.name: Aquarium Drinker
episodes.overview: When a detective is brutally murdered, the Fugitive Task Force investigates a string of gruesome killings. Meanwhile, Remy and Abby's relationship grows stronger.

episodes.name: Varsity Blues
episodes.overview: The Fugitive Task Force is called in to hunt down a missing teen from New Jersey who has a connection to a classmate's recent suicide. Meanwhile, Cora feels Ray and his father are putting too much pressure on Caleb.

episodes.name: White Buffalo
episodes.overview: After a simple act of defiance by a couple of young climate activists goes south, the Fugitive Task Force works to hunt them down before their plans take a devastating turn. Meanwhile, Nina and Scola face family drama when they host her father and sister after they come to town.

episodes.name: Pig Butchering
episodes.overview: As Barnes adjusts to living without her children full time, she and Remy butt heads when she disregards his direct orders and investigates a scam call center from where she received a distressing call from a young girl.

episodes.name: Money Moves
episodes.overview: When a privately owned security corporation warehouse is robbed, the Fugitive Task Force is called in for assistance as the sophisticated team of thieves plan their next heist. Meanwhile, Ray and Cora wrestle with Caleb’s sudden desire to spend time with his biological father.

episodes.name: Pageantry
episodes.overview: When an international beauty queen is killed on live television, the Fugitive Task Force heads to Philadelphia to hunt down the killer. Meanwhile, Hana senses that Ethan is hiding something.

episodes.name: Highway to Hell
episodes.overview: After a Queens district attorney and her husband are executed, the Fugitive Task Force uncovers a money laundering scheme connecting a violent biker gang to Wall Street. Meanwhile, Remy decides to take his relationship with Abby to a new level after he reconnects with an old friend.

episodes.name: The Electric Company
episodes.overview: The Fugitive Task Force clashes with local law enforcement in Virginia while investigating a suspected serial killer in the area. Meanwhile, Remy pushes Abby to take the next step.

episodes.name: Moving On
episodes.overview: The Fugitive Task Force investigates a series of deadly fires involving the descendants of those who caused the infamous 1985 MOVE bombing in Philadelphia. Meanwhile, Nina's sister turns to her in a time of need.

episodes.name: Ars Moriendi
episodes.overview: After witnessing a murder in broad daylight, the Fugitive Task Force must hunt down a team of killers competing in a twisted online game. Meanwhile, Remy and Abby struggle to get on the same page.

episodes.name: Do You Realize??
episodes.overview: The Fugitive Task Force is sent on a hunt in Philadelphia to investigate a double homicide and the abduction of a 14-year-old girl in the foster care system. Meanwhile, Ray’s father is hospitalized after an accident while helping out around the house.

episodes.name: 68 Seconds
episodes.overview: Remy calls in the Fugitive Task Force after ex-girlfriend judge April Brooks is assaulted by a serial rapist. Meanwhile, Remy decides to take the next step in his relationship with Abby after her case in New York winds down.

episodes.name: Greek Tragedy
episodes.overview: When two sorority sisters are found stabbed to death, the Fugitive Task Force heads to Virginia to hunt down the suspect before more killings occur. Hana agrees to meet with Ethan after he asks her for help with his latest troubles.
While helping Ethan seek treatment at a VA Hospital, Hana puts out an SOS to the Fugitive Task Force when she is among those taken hostage by an enraged veteran.

episodes.name: Four Bodies
episodes.overview: A string of late-night murders with the same M.O. sends the Fugitive Task Force on a hunt for a serial killer with ties to a radical feminist group. Meanwhile, Nina's sister asks her for a big favor, causing a strain on Scola and Nina's relationship.

episodes.name: Toxic Behavior
episodes.overview: The Fugitive Task force is called in to connect a series of random poisonings before more lives are lost. Meanwhile, Remy and Abby take on a new project.

episodes.name: Gut Job
episodes.overview: A couple known for their home renovation TV show is thrown into the limelight after the wife is found dead and her husband goes on the run. Meanwhile, Barnes reevaluates her life in New York.

episodes.name: Trust
episodes.overview: The Fugitive Task Force is thrown into the world of the wealthy and twisted after a Rhode Island socialite is murdered in her own mansion. Meanwhile, Barnes contemplates big changes.

episodes.name: Starman
episodes.overview: The Fugitive Task Force investigates the kidnapping of a high-profile astronaut in connection with other disappearances in the area, landing them in the wild world of adult content creators. Meanwhile, Remy and Abby struggle to see eye to eye.

episodes.name: Trash Day
episodes.overview: After a New Jersey mayor is kidnapped, the Fugitive Task Force works against the clock to untangle a web of political conspiracies that may aid their investigation. Meanwhile, Ray’s camping trip with his father and Caleb takes an unexpected turn.

episodes.name: Souls on ICE
episodes.overview: After three men impersonating ICE officers raid a church in New Jersey, the Fugitive Task Force must earn the trust of the reverend to help find the men who were kidnapped. Meanwhile, Remy confronts his own future after learning that Barnes is considering taking a new job.

episodes.name: The Circle Game
episodes.overview: The Fugitive Task Force hunts down a rogue government operative planning a domestic terror attack.
